title: Answering the Toughest Questions About Heaven and Hell - Bickel
description:
Answering the Toughest Questions About Heaven and Hell - Bruce Bickel,Stan Jantz  epub/mobi
ISBN-10: 0764218719   176 pages

When it comes to the big questions about heaven and hell, Bruce Bickel and Stan Jantz don't pretend to have all the answers. But they do know how to wrestle with doubt. They welcome questions, and in these pages they ask some of the most important ones you have about heaven and hell:

· What happens when you die?
· Are heaven and hell for real?
· Do all roads lead to heaven?
· If God is loving, how could he send anyone to hell?
· How do you get into heaven?
· What will heaven and hell be like?
· And more!
